# JETBAY agent context

1. Start from `docs/CONTINUE_AT_HOME.md` and `AGENTS.md` — do not invent status from chat.
2. After meaningful work, update `docs/CONTINUE_AT_HOME.md` and the checklist log.
3. Scope by app: `apps/web` = FE, `apps/api` = BE, `apps/admin` = dashboard. Prefer matching branch prefixes `feat/web-*`, `feat/api-*`, `feat/admin-*`.
4. Features only from `docs/JETBAY_BAO_GIA.md` + `docs/JETBAY_DANH_GIA_KY_THUAT.md`; security patterns may mirror HomeFix but never share secrets/DB with HomeFix.
5. Never commit `.env` / `.env.local` or print production secrets.
6. Shared UI package is `@jetbay/ui` (not `@j-ta/ui`).
